article_title: The Cheap Celeb Finds Of The Week Will Get You Excited For Spring
article_text: As we get increasingly excited for the warmer months ahead, we are fixated on a few celebrities who wore affordable outfits that are going to be perfect for our upcoming vacations. Eva Mendes shone in a $79 floral dress, while Khloe Kardashian just may have found the perfect $92 swimsuit.
